Name":"Organizational, behavioural and financial barriers"},{"id":"cb469aba-1f15-5f6e-bfb6-fa073612150f","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest"}]},{"id":"416d347c-3b3f-530d-8323-4bb4de52b3fe","fullItemName":"References","slug":"references","subChapters":[]}]},"parentChapter":{"id":"82725ef1-b602-5cb0-9269-61529b6c2b02","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},"subChapters":[{"id":"566a1ec2-a22c-5ccf-9307-193f000874fc","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-d58","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field fb688327-1edb-4874-89c5-bb1b74378401 --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field fb688327-1edb-4874-89c5-bb1b74378401 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item d586a561-9342-4679-b577-ba3c3ec088ba --><!-- begin field 68ea35fd-44bf-4e14-ae51-6bc29b3e1dd4 --><p>The recommendations on how to diagnose the cause of breast pain are based on the World Health Organization (WHO) publication <em>Infant and young child feeding - model chapter for textbooks</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/breastfeeding-problems/references/\">WHO, 2009</a>], a review article on breastfeeding problems [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/breastfeeding-problems/references/\">Amir, 2014</a>], and the US Academy of Breastfeeding Medicine clinical protocols <em>Persistent pain with breastfeeding</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/breastfeeding-problems/references/\">Berens et al, 2016</a>] and <em>Engorgement</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/breastfeeding-problems/references/\">Berens, 2016</a>].</p><!-- end field 68ea35fd-44bf-4e14-ae51-6bc29b3e1dd4 --><!-- end item d586a561-9342-4679-b577-ba3c3ec088ba -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}